Name: Mediterranean Diet
Description: High in vegetables, fruits, nuts, and whole grains.

Name: Intermittent Fasting
Description: Eating patterns that cycle between periods of fasting and eating.

Name: DASH Diet
Description: Emphasizes vegetables, fruits, and low-fat dairy.

Name: Paleo Diet
Description: Focuses on foods similar to what might have been eaten during the Paleolithic era.

Name: Gluten-Free Diet
Description: Excludes gluten, a protein found in wheat, barley, and rye.
